:

1. *Daću* ti sve što tražiš. (I will give you everything you ask for.)
2. *Daj* mi jedan razlog zašto treba da to uradim. (Give me one reason why I should do that.)
3. *Dao* sam joj očigledno previše pažnje. (I obviously gave her too much attention.)
4. *Daću* ti odgovor kada budem spreman. (I will give you an answer when I am ready.)